<p>The current medical model is based on the treatment of symptoms once a disease arises. If we want to live healthier lives, we need to work on preventing the diseases that lead to a decrease in healthspan and lifespan—cardiovascular disease, metabolic dysfunction, cancer, and neurodegenerative disease.</p>
