<p>This book has made me shift my view on my working life. It has been ingrained in our culture that working a good 9-5 job will allow us to make money that we can spend on accumulating more things. Well, to make money we don’t need to sell our time for money, we can set up a system that allows us to make money without being strapped down to a single job every day.</p>
